==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incroyable
<hw>In`croy`a"ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., lit.,
incredible.]</ety> <def>A French fop or dandy of the time of the
Directory; hence, any fop.</def></p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is said to have been given in allusion not only
to the extravagant dress, but also to the frequent use of the phrase
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>C'est vraiment incroyable</xex>⟦rdquo⟧ (That is really
incredible.).</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incruental</ent>⟦br⟧
